<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.1.10">
<l>pūmaru poḻilaṇi viṇṇakarmēl</l>
<l>kāmaru cīrkkali kaṉṟicoṉṉa</l>
<l>pāmaru tamiḻivai pāṭavallār</l>
<l>vāmaṉa ṉaṭiyiṇai maruvuvarē.</l>
<l rend="indent">āṇṭāyuṉaik kāṇpatō raruḷeṉak karuḷutiyēl</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭēṉmaṉai vāḻkkaiyai viṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are able to sing these poetic Tamil [verses]</l>
<l>Which Kalikaṉṟi of desired esteem composed</l>
<l>On beautiful Viṇṇakar adorned with flower-scented gardens,</l>
<l>Will embrace both feet of Vāmana;</l>
<l rend="indent">Master, if you bless me with the one blessing of seeing you,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not want this domestic life, you who dwells in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
